ject.&#160;</p><p><strong>&#8220;I was saying things in songs that female singers didn&#8217;t really say back then. I wasn&#8217;t submissive or begging him to come back, I was kicking his ass, kicking him out, kicking my own ass too. My Blondie character was an inflatable doll but with a dark, provocative, aggressive side. I was playing it&#160;up&#160;yet I was very serious.&#8221;&#8212;From&#160;<em>Face It&#160;</em></strong></p>
